UPDATE ODS_AIMS_ACCOUNT A SET A.HT_E_DT = A.HT_S_DT
    WHERE (A.ACCOUNTNO, A.CLTNO, A.BRANCH_BANK_NO) NOT IN
          (SELECT A1.ACCOUNTNO, A1.CLTNO, A1.BRANCH_BANK_NO
             FROM STG_AIMS_ACCOUNT A1 WHERE A1.SJRQ = TO_CHAR(TRUNC(SYSDATE)-1,'yyyy-MM-dd'))
          AND A.HT_E_DT = DATE'3000-12-31' ;
